{"id": "6481", "revid": "6540498", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6481", "title": "Logan's Catalyst", "text": "Logan's Catalyst is a &lt;a href=\"catalysts\"&gt;catalyst&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound in a chest in a small library room in &lt;a href=\"The%20Duke%27s%20Archives\"&gt;The Duke's Archives&lt;/a&gt;, the same room where &lt;a href=\"Big%20Hat%20Logan\"&gt;Big Hat Logan&lt;/a&gt; moves to and sells his wares after being freed from the prison cell. The chest will only spawn after Big Hat Logan has gone insane and relocated to the upper chambers of the archives, where &lt;a href=\"Seath%20the%20Scaleless\"&gt;Seath the Scaleless&lt;/a&gt; is initially found.\nCharacteristics.\nLogan's catalyst is one of the best catalysts to use at higher intelligence levels. At 41 &lt;a href=\"Intelligence%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt; and beyond, the only catalysts with higher magic adjust are &lt;a href=\"Tin%20Crystallization%20Catalyst\"&gt;Tin Crystallization Catalyst&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Manus%20Catalyst\"&gt;Manus Catalyst&lt;/a&gt;, though both of these Catalysts halve spell casts making Logan's have superior damage potential unless going for a one-shot build. Logan's Catalyst initially has inferior magic adjust than other catalysts but catches up later thanks to its great scaling.\nMagic Adjust.\nLogan's Catalyst starts with a low 100 Magic Adjust at 24 intelligence. It will have a great scaling of 12 Magic Adjust per point of intelligence from 26-30 intelligence, where it will hit a minor soft cap at 160 Magic Adjust. Its scaling will then go down to increments of 5 Magic Adjust per intelligence, all the way to 45 intelligence, where it will have 235 Magic Adjust. It will overtake the other \"normal\" catalysts at 41 intelligence. Past 45 intelligence, Logan's Catalyst will have insignificant improvements from scaling."}
