{"id": "130256", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=130256", "title": "Long Sword", "text": "The Long Sword is a &lt;a href=\"Straight%20Swords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;straight sword&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nThe Long Sword is among the most versatile weapons in the game. It is useful in most situations and its low stat requirements and weight allows it to be wielded by most starting classes given some light stat investments. It features broad slashes and quick thrusting attacks, allowing it to stay effective in a multitude of engagements that bigger or less versatile weapons may struggle with.\nAdditionally, the Long Sword also performs well with infusions and can stay competitive with many heavy weapons in spite of its status as a jack-of-all-trades. With its speed allowing for much more frequent hits, it is especially effective against more agile targets. However the weapon is rather poor for trading hits as it struggles to both use poise and break it.\nFurthermore, the &lt;a href=\"Stance%20%28Straight%20Sword%29\"&gt;Stance&lt;/a&gt; grants the weapon some extra mobility and reach, and allows it to go up against shields effectively. A well timed shield break will guard break all but the toughest shields with relative ease, in both PvE and PvP. However, the slow attacks can be dodged easily if the enemy is ready to react.\nUpgrades.\nReinforced with &lt;a href=\"Upgrade%20Materials%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Titanite&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "4774", "revid": "56333033", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4774", "title": "Longbow", "text": "The Longbow is a &lt;a href=\"Bows\"&gt;bow&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nThe Longbow has the same range as the &lt;a href=\"Short%20Bow\"&gt;Short Bow&lt;/a&gt; and deals slightly more damage. In exchange, it requires slightly higher &lt;a href=\"Strength%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dexterity%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt; to wield. It is also of \"Long Bow\" category, giving it a slightly lower rate of fire.\nWhile it has a lower scaling with dexterity than the &lt;a href=\"Black%20Bow%20of%20Pharis\"&gt;Black Bow of Pharis&lt;/a&gt;, it will usually out damage it, thanks to its higher base damage and strength scaling.\nUpgrades.\nScaling Percentage Values.\nThe following chart lists the scaling percentages when this weapon is fully upgraded. Be advised that:"}
