{"id": "4935", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4935", "title": "Lord's Blade Ciaran", "text": "Lord's Blade Ciaran (\u738b\u306e\u5203 \u30ad\u30a2\u30e9\u30f3) is a &lt;a href=\"characters\"&gt;character&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\". She is exclusive to the \"&lt;a href=\"Artorias%20of%20the%20Abyss\"&gt;Artorias of the Abyss&lt;/a&gt;\" DLC. She is voiced by , who also voices &lt;a href=\"Sweet%20Shalquoir\"&gt;Sweet Shalquoir&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLocation.\nFound in the coliseum of &lt;a href=\"Oolacile%20Township\"&gt;Oolacile Township&lt;/a&gt; after defeating &lt;a href=\"Artorias%20the%20Abysswalker\"&gt;Knight Artorias&lt;/a&gt;.\nPlot.\nCiaran appears after Artorias is defeated, asking the player for the &lt;a href=\"Soul%20of%20Artorias\"&gt;Soul of Artorias&lt;/a&gt;. She rewards the player with the &lt;a href=\"Gold%20Tracer\"&gt;Gold Tracer&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Silver%20Tracer\"&gt;Dark Silver Tracer&lt;/a&gt; if given the Soul of Artorias.\nLore.\nShe is the only female among the &lt;a href=\"Four%20Knights%20of%20Gwyn\"&gt;Four Knights of Gwyn&lt;/a&gt; and owner of the &lt;a href=\"Hornet%20Ring\"&gt;Hornet Ring&lt;/a&gt;; she wore it while using her dagger to lay waste to her foes.\nStrategy.\nCiaran utilizes &lt;a href=\"Throwing%20Knife\"&gt;Throwing Knives&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Lloyd%27s%20Talisman\"&gt;Lloyd's Talisman&lt;/a&gt;s. Her attacks can be quite damaging given their speed and &lt;a href=\"Toxic%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Toxic&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; buildup, and she has much more health than the average NPC."}
