{"id": "8198", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8198", "title": "Lord's Blade Set", "text": "The Lord's Blade Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\". It is only available in the \"&lt;a href=\"Artorias%20of%20the%20Abyss\"&gt;Artorias of the Abyss&lt;/a&gt;\"\u00a0DLC. \nAvailability.\nDropped by &lt;a href=\"Lord%27s%20Blade%20Ciaran\"&gt;Lord's Blade Ciaran&lt;/a&gt;.\nPlot.\nWorn by the Lord's Blades. However, the mask is unique to Ciaran.\nCharacteristics.\nThis set is light and offers little &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0(although &lt;a href=\"Weight\"&gt;heavier&lt;/a&gt; and offering more protection and poise than most cloth sets), and is good for builds that require mobility and don't care much about defense. It's most notable for its &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Poison&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; resistances."}
