{"id": "131797", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=131797", "title": "Lorian's Greatsword", "text": "Lorian's Greatsword is a &lt;a href=\"Boss%20Soul%20Items%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;soul-transposed&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Ultra%20Greatswords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;ultra greatsword&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nObtained by transposing the &lt;a href=\"Soul%20of%20the%20Twin%20Princes\"&gt;Soul of the Twin Princes&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Ludleth%20of%20Courland\"&gt;Ludleth of Courland&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nLorian's Greatsword is notable for being the only ultra greatsword in the game that inflicts meaningful amounts of &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; damage. While it has no &lt;a href=\"Intelligence%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Faith%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Faith&lt;/a&gt; wielding requirements, it scales with both stats, making it a good weapon for quality builds that tend towards &lt;a href=\"Strength%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; but which also invest into caster stats.\nLorian's Greatsword utilizes the horizontal swinging ultra greatsword moveset, similar to the &lt;a href=\"Profaned%20Greatsword\"&gt;Profaned Greatsword&lt;/a&gt;, while combining it with thrusts and vertical swings to bring focused single-target damage to the table. This is further enhanced by its &lt;a href=\"skill\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;, which can be used to devastate single enemies and to further enhance the Fire damage it deals."}
