{"id": "135808", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135808", "title": "Lucatiel's Mask (Dark Souls III)", "text": "Lucatiel's Mask is a piece in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\". It is part of the &lt;a href=\"Mirrah%20Set\"&gt;Mirrah Set&lt;/a&gt;.\nAvailability.\nObtained once per playthrough by trading a &lt;a href=\"Vertebra%20Shackle\"&gt;Vertebra Shackle&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Pickle%20Pee\"&gt;Pickle Pee&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Firelink%20Shrine%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Firelink Shrine&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "75184", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=75184", "title": "Lucatiel's Set", "text": " is a\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nGift from\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Lucatiel%20of%20Mirrah\"&gt;Lucatiel of Mirrah&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in &lt;a href=\"Aldia%27s%20Keep\"&gt;Aldia's Keep&lt;/a&gt; if she survived three of her boss fights as a summon.\u00a0Alternatively, Lucatiel can be killed in any location and her set bought off\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Merchant%20Hag%20Melentia\"&gt;Merchant Hag Melentia&lt;/a&gt; for 18,000 &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nLucatiel's Set has an interesting blend of protection; the set provides absolutely no &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt;, but it boasts decent &lt;a href=\"physical\"&gt;physical&lt;/a&gt; defenses, &lt;a href=\"durability\"&gt;durability&lt;/a&gt;, excellent &lt;a href=\"elemental\"&gt;elemental&lt;/a&gt; defenses, and good &lt;a href=\"resistance\"&gt;resistance&lt;/a&gt;s.\nWhile it does not provide any Poise, it provides excellent elemental defenses and a high resistance to every auxiliary effect when the set is fully-&lt;a href=\"reinforce\"&gt;reinforce&lt;/a&gt;d.\nIt upgrades with regular &lt;a href=\"Titanite%20Shard%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;titanite&lt;/a&gt;."}
