{"id": "4324", "revid": "51254358", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4324", "title": "Magic Barrier", "text": "Magic Barrier (\u9b54\u6cd5\u9632\u8b77) is a &lt;a href=\"Miracle%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;miracle&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nMagic Barrier is sold by &lt;a href=\"Reah%20of%20Thorolund\"&gt;Reah of Thorolund&lt;/a&gt; for 6,000 &lt;a href=\"soul\"&gt;soul&lt;/a&gt;s after rescuing her from the &lt;a href=\"Tomb%20of%20the%20Giants\"&gt;Tomb of the Giants&lt;/a&gt;.\nGeneral information.\nMagic Barrier applies a defensive buff to the caster that lasts for 40 seconds and reduces &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;magic&lt;/a&gt; damage taken by 30%. The damage reduction applies to all offensive &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;sorceries&lt;/a&gt;, offensive &lt;a href=\"Miracle%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;miracles&lt;/a&gt;, and any weapon that deals magic damage. Magic Barrier counts as a personal buff, so it is impossible to use other buffs (such as &lt;a href=\"Power%20Within\"&gt;Power Within&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Flash%20Sweat\"&gt;Flash Sweat&lt;/a&gt;, etc.) while it is in effect.\n&lt;a href=\"Great%20Magic%20Barrier\"&gt;Great Magic Barrier&lt;/a&gt; is an upgrade over Magic Barrier, boasting higher magic resistance in exchange for fewer casts.\nDescription.\n&lt;tabber&gt;Official translation=\n&lt;/tabber&gt;"}
{"id": "71896", "revid": "56333033", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=71896", "title": "Magic Barrier (Dark Souls II)", "text": "Magic Barrier is a &lt;a href=\"Miracles%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;miracle&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nEffect.\nThis miracle casts an aura around its user, causing them to become extra resistant towards &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt; attacks by 150. The duration of this spell depends on Faith and ranges from 70 seconds when spiced down to 10 Faith all the way up to 95 seconds at 34 Faith which caps the duration scaling. In addition, Magic Barrier can affect allied players within a certain radius. This trait is not shared by &lt;a href=\"Great%20Magic%20Barrier%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Great Magic Barrier&lt;/a&gt;.\nAttunement Milestones.\nLike all other spells, the amount of casts per slot increases upon reaching certain &lt;a href=\"Attunement%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Attunement&lt;/a&gt; milestones:\nDuration Scaling Information.\nDuration values are listed in seconds. Base duration of this spell only depends on Faith. Base duration shown as well as values with the &lt;a href=\"Lingering%20Dragoncrest%20Ring%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Lingering Dragoncrest&lt;/a&gt; variants applied and pieces of &lt;a href=\"Northwarder%20Set\"&gt;Northwarder Set&lt;/a&gt; applied. This self buff has non-scaling ranges which is why the duration does not go up with each level of Faith. "}
{"id": "133500", "revid": "51254358", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=133500", "title": "Magic Barrier (Dark Souls III)", "text": "Magic Barrier (\u9b54\u529b\u9632\u8b77) is a &lt;a href=\"Miracle%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;miracle&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nSold by &lt;a href=\"Irina%20of%20Carim\"&gt;Irina of Carim&lt;/a&gt; for 5,000 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; once she has been given the &lt;a href=\"Braille%20Divine%20Tome%20of%20Lothric\"&gt;Braille Divine Tome of Lothric&lt;/a&gt;.\nEffect.\nIncreases &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; absorption by 35%. Buff lasts for 90 seconds, or 1 minute and 30 seconds.\nUnlike most other buffs, this value is the same in &lt;a href=\"Player%20versus%20Player%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;PvP&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\n&lt;tabber&gt;Official translation=\n&lt;/tabber&gt;"}
