{"id": "15231", "revid": "33084951", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=15231", "title": "Magic Upgrade Path", "text": ""}
{"id": "4630", "revid": "37406887", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4630", "title": "Magic Weapon", "text": "Magic Weapon (\u9b54\u6cd5\u306e\u6b66\u5668) is a &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Sorcery&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nGeneral information.\nMagic Weapon may only be used on enchantable weapons, which are those that are upgraded down the &lt;a href=\"Standard%20%28upgrade%20path%29\"&gt;Standard&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Raw%20%28upgrade%20path%29\"&gt;Raw&lt;/a&gt;, or &lt;a href=\"Crystal%20%28upgrade%20path%29\"&gt;Crystal&lt;/a&gt; paths, as well as a limited amount of &lt;a href=\"Weapon%20Augmentation%23Non-standard%20weapons\"&gt;exceptions&lt;/a&gt;.\nMagic Weapon is a &lt;a href=\"weapon%20augmentation\"&gt;weapon augmentation&lt;/a&gt;, temporarily adding &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Magic Damage&lt;/a&gt; to the right hand weapon. It adds a flat amount of magic attack power to the weapon equal to 0.8 times the catalyst's magic adjust. It becomes inferior once other augmentation &lt;a href=\"Great%20Magic%20Weapon\"&gt;sorceries&lt;/a&gt; are acquired.\nDescription.\n&lt;tabber&gt;Official translation=\n&lt;/tabber&gt;"}
{"id": "65780", "revid": "56333033", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=65780", "title": "Magic Weapon (Dark Souls II)", "text": "Magic Weapon is a &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;sorcery&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nBought for 2,000 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=\"Carhillion%20of%20the%20Fold\"&gt;Carhillion of the Fold&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"No-man%27s%20Wharf\"&gt;No-man's Wharf&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Majula\"&gt;Majula&lt;/a&gt;.\nEffect.\nApplies a &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; buff to the weapon in the hand opposite the &lt;a href=\"Staves\"&gt;staff&lt;/a&gt; used to cast the spell. Though it is weaker than the &lt;a href=\"Great%20Magic%20Weapon%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Great&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Crystal%20Magic%20Weapon%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Crystal&lt;/a&gt; variants, Magic Weapon's high amount of casts, long duration, and low requirements means it can serve to boost a player's damage output throughout entire areas instead of needing to be saved for single engagements or boss fights. \nThe total bonus is difficult to calculate, but is roughly 15% of the sum (30 + weapon's Magic scaling * character's Magic bonus + weapon's Base damage), with a small additional damage bonus on &lt;a href=\"Faintstone\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; infused weapons. \nThe duration scales with Intelligence, starting at 63 seconds at the 10 required Intelligence all the way up to 135 seconds at 15 Intelligence where the duration scaling caps. \nAttunement Milestones.\nLike all other spells, the amount of casts per slot increases upon reaching certain &lt;a href=\"Attunement%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Attunement&lt;/a&gt; milestones:\nDuration Scaling Information.\nDuration values are listed in seconds. Base duration of this spell only depends on Intelligence. Base duration shown as well as values with the &lt;a href=\"Lingering%20Dragoncrest%20Ring%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Lingering Dragoncrest&lt;/a&gt; variants applied and pieces of &lt;a href=\"Northwarder%20Set\"&gt;Northwarder Set&lt;/a&gt; applied.\u00a0 \u00a0 "}
{"id": "133912", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=133912", "title": "Magic Weapon (Dark Souls III)", "text": "Magic Weapon is a &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;sorcery&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nEffect.\nReinforces right-hand &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;weapon&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt;, adding 75% of the &lt;a href=\"Catalysts%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;catalyst's&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Buff\"&gt;Spell Buff&lt;/a&gt; as Magic damage for 90 seconds. This duration can be extended by equipping the &lt;a href=\"Lingering%20Dragoncrest%20Ring%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Lingering Dragoncrest Ring&lt;/a&gt;.\nFor catalysts that scale with both &lt;a href=\"Intelligence%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Faith%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Faith&lt;/a&gt;, only the Intelligence portion of the Spell Buff is counted. Special catalysts such as the &lt;a href=\"Archdeacon%27s%20Great%20Staff\"&gt;Archdeacon's Great Staff&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Man-grub%27s%20Staff\"&gt;Man-grub's Staff&lt;/a&gt; are treated as having the base 100 Spell Buff.\n&lt;br&gt;"}
{"id": "177574", "revid": "27795815", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=177574", "title": "Magic adjust", "text": ""}
{"id": "177543", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=177543", "title": "Magic adjustment", "text": " Magic adjustment (abbreviated in-game as MagAdjust) is a &lt;a href=\"Stats%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;stat&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\" specific to &lt;a href=\"catalysts\"&gt;catalysts&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"talismans\"&gt;talismans&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Pyromancy%20Flame\"&gt;pyromancy flame&lt;/a&gt;s.\nEffect.\nMagic adjustment acts as a base value for the damage and effect magnitude of spells cast by the respective tool. For example, casting the &lt;a href=\"pyromancy\"&gt;pyromancy&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Fireball\"&gt;Fireball&lt;/a&gt; with a pyromancy flame deals base &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;fire damage&lt;/a&gt; equal to two times the pyromancy flame's magic adjustment. (This damage is further modified by enemy stats, such as flame defense.)\nFor most catalysts and talismans, magic adjustment &lt;a href=\"Scaling\"&gt;scales&lt;/a&gt; with the caster's stats, usually &lt;a href=\"Intelligence%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;intelligence&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Faith%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;faith&lt;/a&gt;. Exceptions are the &lt;a href=\"Oolacile%20Catalyst\"&gt;Oolacile Catalyst&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Oolacile%20Ivory%20Catalyst\"&gt;Oolacile Ivory Catalyst&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Thorolund%20Talisman\"&gt;Thorolund Talisman&lt;/a&gt;, where each has static magic adjustment. For the pyromancy flames, magic adjustment scales with the flame's &lt;a href=\"Weapon%20Reinforcement\"&gt;reinforcement&lt;/a&gt; level."}
