{"id": "8127", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8127", "title": "Maiden Set", "text": "The Maiden Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nPlot.\nThe Maiden Set is worn by traveling maidens. The one found by the player is likely left over from a maiden captured for Seath's experiments.\nCharacteristics.\nThis set offers little defense and no &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt;,\u00a0but is light weight and gives decent &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;curse&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0resistance. Upgrading the set will considerably improve its defenses; however, its resistances will not improve at all until to +4."}
{"id": "135204", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135204", "title": "Maiden Set (Dark Souls III)", "text": "The Maiden Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound on a corpse in the &lt;a href=\"Cathedral%20of%20the%20Deep\"&gt;Cathedral of the Deep&lt;/a&gt;, at the feet of a &lt;a href=\"Giant%20Slave\"&gt;Giant Slave&lt;/a&gt; in the murky pool farthest away from the &lt;a href=\"Deacons%20of%20the%20Deep\"&gt;Deacons of the Deep&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nLike other cloth sets, the Maiden Set provides poor defense against &lt;a href=\"physical%20damage\"&gt;physical damage&lt;/a&gt; and does not resist &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"buildup\"&gt;buildup&lt;/a&gt; well. However, it does have notably high &lt;a href=\"elemental%20resistance\"&gt;elemental resistance&lt;/a&gt; as well as very high &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; resistance."}
