{"id": "55894", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=55894", "title": "Malformed Shell", "text": "The Malformed Shell\u00a0is a &lt;a href=\"Great%20Hammers%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;great hammer&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound behind a wall in &lt;a href=\"Aldia%27s%20Keep\"&gt;Aldia's Keep&lt;/a&gt;. To get the weapon, the player must lure an &lt;a href=\"Ogre\"&gt;Ogre&lt;/a&gt; into attacking a heavily chained gate to break it, revealing a chest containing the weapon."}
