{"id": "63768", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=63768", "title": "Manikin", "text": "Manikins, also known as Masked Manikins, are a type of in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLocation.\nThey are found in &lt;a href=\"Earthen%20Peak\"&gt;Earthen Peak&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nThere are four variations of this enemy; the variations wield daggers, sabres, bows or claws. What they lack in raw power, they make up for in speed.\nStrategy.\nUnless the player can act faster than them, a high &lt;a href=\"stability\"&gt;stability&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Shields%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;shield&lt;/a&gt; is recommended. Wait for them to strike, then counter with a high-damaging weapon. They are certainly more threatening in numbers."}
