{"id": "61250", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=61250", "title": "Manikin Sabre", "text": "The Manikin Sabre\u00a0is a &lt;a href=\"Curved%20Swords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;curved sword&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nThe Manikin Sabre is a rare drop from sabre-wielding &lt;a href=\"Manikin\"&gt;Manikin&lt;/a&gt;s. Three Manikins are located just outside of the &lt;a href=\"Central%20Earthen%20Peak\"&gt;Central Earthen Peak&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;bonfire&lt;/a&gt;, and an additional one just past the gate above the same bonfire.\nCharacteristics.\nLike all other Manikin weapons, this curved sword has a special feature that allows it to actually gain a significant amount of damage when &lt;a href=\"infuse\"&gt;infuse&lt;/a&gt;d, as only the &lt;a href=\"Scaling%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;scaling&lt;/a&gt; will be reduced."}
