{"id": "55586", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=55586", "title": "Manikin Shield", "text": "The Manikin Shield\u00a0is a &lt;a href=\"Small%20Shields%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;small shield&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nChance to be dropped by &lt;a href=\"Manikin\"&gt;Manikin&lt;/a&gt;s in &lt;a href=\"Earthen%20Peak\"&gt;Earthen Peak&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nThe Manikin Shield has fairly high &lt;a href=\"physical%20damage\"&gt;physical damage&lt;/a&gt; reduction for a small shield, but quite low &lt;a href=\"elemental\"&gt;elemental&lt;/a&gt; resistances. The shield does, however, have above average &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Poison&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Petrification%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Petrification&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; reduction in relation to its light &lt;a href=\"weight\"&gt;weight&lt;/a&gt;, making it a good choice for characters with low &lt;a href=\"Vitality%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Vitality&lt;/a&gt; in areas where\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Negative%20Status%20Effects%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;negative status effects&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0are common."}
