{"id": "51704", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=51704", "title": "Mastodon Greatsword", "text": "The Mastodon Greatsword is a &lt;a href=\"Greatswords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;greatsword&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nLike the &lt;a href=\"Mastodon%20Halberd\"&gt;Mastodon Halberd&lt;/a&gt;, this weapon inflicts more &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt; damage than the other weapons of its class usually can inflict. However, it comes at the cost of being tremendously heavy (rivaling the weight of other heavy weapons), making it unpopular to those who do not invest much in their &lt;a href=\"Vitality%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Vitality&lt;/a&gt; stat, as well as a high &lt;a href=\"Strength%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; requirement to be wielded effectively.\nOn the other hand, this weapon has great potential for strength-oriented builds, as well as possessing a very versatile moveset of horizontal and vertical slashes, making it a great, lighter alternative to other heavier weapons with similar traits, such as the &lt;a href=\"Greatsword%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Greatsword&lt;/a&gt;."}
