{"id": "133473", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=133473", "title": "Med Heal (Dark Souls III)", "text": "Med Heal is a &lt;a href=\"Miracle%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;miracle&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nEffect.\nRestores &lt;a href=\"Hit%20Points%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;HP&lt;/a&gt; for the caster and nearby allies equal to 4.1 times the &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Buff\"&gt;Spell Buff&lt;/a&gt; of the catalyst, and consumes 123 &lt;a href=\"Endurance%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;stamina&lt;/a&gt;. For catalysts that also scale with &lt;a href=\"Intelligence%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt; such as &lt;a href=\"Crystal%20Chime\"&gt;Crystal Chime&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Sunless%20Talisman\"&gt;Sunless Talisman&lt;/a&gt;, only the Spell Buff from &lt;a href=\"Faith%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Faith&lt;/a&gt; is taken into account.\nThis is the highest tier instant-heal Miracle that does not completely deplete the stamina bar of the caster upon completion. Thus, it allows for action immediately after the spell ends, such as rolling to evade incoming danger.\n&lt;br&gt;"}
