{"id": "103486", "revid": "26269363", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=103486", "title": "Pyromancer Set", "text": "The Pyromancer Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nA cloth set, the Pyromancer Set is quite light, and offers little in the way of &lt;a href=\"physical%20defense\"&gt;physical defense&lt;/a&gt;s. It has strong &lt;a href=\"elemental\"&gt;elemental&lt;/a&gt; absorption, being particularly effective at warding off &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt; damage. It does not tolerate &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; buildup well, but is fairly resistant to &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Poison&lt;/a&gt; and very effective against &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "136121", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=136121", "title": "Pyromancer Trousers", "text": "The Pyromancer Trousers are in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\". They are part of the &lt;a href=\"Pyromancer%20Set\"&gt;Pyromancer Set&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "136120", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=136120", "title": "Pyromancer Wrap", "text": "The Pyromancer Wrap is a in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\". It is part of the &lt;a href=\"Pyromancer%20Set\"&gt;Pyromancer Set&lt;/a&gt;."}
