{"id": "98974", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=98974", "title": "Rampart Golem", "text": "Rampart Golems are &lt;a href=\"Enemies%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;enemies&lt;/a&gt; in .\nLore.\nLong ago, these knights were charged with the containment of the creatures of &lt;a href=\"chaos\"&gt;chaos&lt;/a&gt; within the boundaries of &lt;a href=\"Eleum%20Loyce\"&gt;Eleum Loyce&lt;/a&gt;. When the doors of city were flung open, the place turned frigid and lifeless, but the &lt;a href=\"golems\"&gt;golems&lt;/a&gt; remained dutifully on guard.\nLocation.\nFound all across &lt;a href=\"Frozen%20Eleum%20Loyce\"&gt;Frozen Eleum Loyce&lt;/a&gt;. Specifically, one directly behind the gate guarded by a &lt;a href=\"Spellsword\"&gt;Spellsword&lt;/a&gt; who will be shooting from the embrasure to your right; two more after that will be to both sides of the first, one guarding the door to the Expulsion chamber bonfire and the other being on the spiral stairs. The next golem is encountered after the &lt;a href=\"Wall%20Watchman\"&gt;Wall watchmen&lt;/a&gt; zone, after passing a lone &lt;a href=\"Retainer\"&gt;Retainer&lt;/a&gt; and an ambushing spear Spellsword. One is guarding a chamber with a &lt;a href=\"Knight%20of%20Eleum%20Loyce\"&gt;Knight of Eleum Loyce&lt;/a&gt; after the zone with wooden scaffolds and after the invading &lt;a href=\"Castaway%20Witch%20Donna\"&gt;Castaway Witch Donna&lt;/a&gt;. One is guarding yet another chamber with a Knight of Eleum Loyce in the zone with Ice golems and a rollable snowball to cover the gap in the bridge. Two next to each other are found in an area accountable to the Inner wall bonfire after passing through the hidden door and proceeding behind (they can be aggroed separately if caution is maintained). Finally, one golem is found surrounded by barrels in the third ruined bulding of &lt;a href=\"Frigid%20Outskirts\"&gt;Frigid Outskirts&lt;/a&gt;. A total of no more than 9 Rampart golems can be found at any given moment in-game."}
