{"id": "5370", "revid": "5064773", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5370", "title": "Raw (upgrade path)", "text": "Raw is an &lt;a href=\"upgrade%20path\"&gt;upgrade path&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nRaw is available as an upgrade path for blacksmith &lt;a href=\"Andre%20of%20Astora\"&gt;Andre of Astora&lt;/a&gt; after he is given the &lt;a href=\"Large%20Ember\"&gt;Large Ember&lt;/a&gt;. Uniquely for an &lt;a href=\"Weapon%20Modification\"&gt;ascension path&lt;/a&gt;, Raw requires only &lt;a href=\"Large%20Titanite%20Shard\"&gt;Large Titanite Shard&lt;/a&gt;s as &lt;a href=\"upgrade%20materials\"&gt;upgrade materials&lt;/a&gt;, as well as a &lt;a href=\"standard%20weapon\"&gt;standard weapon&lt;/a&gt; +5 and the requisite &lt;a href=\"souls\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt;.\nOverview.\nRaw increases the base damage of a &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;weapon&lt;/a&gt;, while reducing its stat scaling from &lt;a href=\"Strength%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dexterity%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt;. As its name suggests, it gives the weapon jagged edges, making it more dangerous but also more unwieldy.\nIt is a unique upgrade path in that it does not allow a second tier of ascension. It essentially functions as a way for players to maximize their attack power early on in the game, with Raw +5 weapons generally more powerful than Normal +10 weapons. However, Normal +15 weapons are always stronger than their Raw +5 counterparts."}
{"id": "130394", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=130394", "title": "Raw Gem", "text": "Raw Gems are in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nUsage.\nWhen infusing a weapon with Raw, the weapon gains greatly increased base damage, but loses any and all &lt;a href=\"Parameter%20Bonus%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;scaling&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Strength%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dexterity%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "67853", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=67853", "title": "Raw Stone", "text": "Raw Stone is an\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Upgrade%20Materials%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;upgrade material&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nThe Raw Stone can be\u00a0used to &lt;a href=\"infuse\"&gt;infuse&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;weapons&lt;/a&gt;. It increases the base damage of the weapon but severely lowers its current &lt;a href=\"Scaling%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;scaling&lt;/a&gt; and cannot be used on\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Shields%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;shields&lt;/a&gt;."}
