{"id": "3221", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3221", "title": "Red &amp; White Round Shield", "text": "The Red &amp; White Round Shield is a &lt;a href=\"small%20shield\"&gt;small shield&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nThe Red &amp; White Round Shield is dropped by &lt;a href=\"Skeleton\"&gt;Skeleton&lt;/a&gt;s located in the &lt;a href=\"Firelink%20Shrine\"&gt;Firelink Shrine&lt;/a&gt; graveyard and &lt;a href=\"The%20Catacombs\"&gt;The Catacombs&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Red &amp; White Round Shield shares the same characteristics as the &lt;a href=\"Warrior%27s%20Round%20Shield\"&gt;Warrior's Round Shield&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Caduceus%20Round%20Shield\"&gt;Caduceus Round Shield&lt;/a&gt;. It has good &lt;a href=\"magic%20defense\"&gt;magic defense&lt;/a&gt; and is quite &lt;a href=\"Weight\"&gt;light&lt;/a&gt;. However, because of its 85 &lt;a href=\"physical%20defense\"&gt;physical defense&lt;/a&gt;, it's impractical for any situation that does not call for magic defense. It has light deflection and a fast &lt;a href=\"parry\"&gt;parry&lt;/a&gt; animation. When &lt;a href=\"Weapon%20Modification\"&gt;upgraded&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"Crystal%20%28upgrade%20path%29\"&gt;crystal&lt;/a&gt; the &lt;a href=\"durability\"&gt;durability&lt;/a&gt; is 18.\nResistance defense.\nAlong with Physical and &lt;a href=\"Elemental\"&gt;Elemental&lt;/a&gt; damage reduction, weapons also have hidden stats that reduce the amount of status &lt;a href=\"build-up\"&gt;build-up&lt;/a&gt; while blocking."}
