{"id": "2982", "revid": "357163", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2982", "title": "Red Tearstone Ring", "text": "The Red Tearstone Ring is a combat-oriented &lt;a href=\"Rings%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;ring&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nLocated on top of the tower between the &lt;a href=\"Valley%20of%20Drakes\"&gt;Valley of Drakes&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"New%20Londo%20Ruins\"&gt;New Londo Ruins&lt;/a&gt;.\nEffect.\nBoosts all attack power by 50% when user has less than 20% health. This offensive boost to applies to almost all forms of dealing damage, including &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;sorceries&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Pyromancy%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;pyromancies&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Miracle%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;miracles&lt;/a&gt;, but not to throwable items like &lt;a href=\"Throwing%20Knife\"&gt;Throwing Knives&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Firebomb\"&gt;Firebomb&lt;/a&gt;s.\nOverview.\nAnalogous to the &lt;a href=\"w%3Ac%3Ademonssouls%3AClever%20Rat%27s%20Ring\"&gt;Clever Rat's Ring&lt;/a&gt; from \"&lt;a href=\"Demon%27s%20Souls\"&gt;Demon's Souls&lt;/a&gt;\". The Red Tearstone Ring sees much less use than its counterpart due to the absence of an insurance spell such as Second Chance. However, extra skillful players may get use out of this ring yet as its damage boost is very significant. The ring stacks with other damage boosters, so particularly suicidal players can try using both this ring and &lt;a href=\"Power%20Within\"&gt;Power Within&lt;/a&gt; for a dramatic, but short-lived, boost. The Red Tearstone Ring can be used well with the &lt;a href=\"Blue%20Tearstone%20Ring\"&gt;Blue Tearstone Ring&lt;/a&gt; if the player has high defense and vitality."}
{"id": "31234", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=31234", "title": "Red Tearstone Ring (Dark Souls II)", "text": "The Red Tearstone Ring is a &lt;a href=\"Rings%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;ring&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound in the &lt;a href=\"Shaded%20Woods\"&gt;Shaded Woods&lt;/a&gt;, in a pool of water before the door to &lt;a href=\"Aldia%27s%20Keep\"&gt;Aldia's Keep&lt;/a&gt;.\nEffect.\nThis ring increases the damage of attacks, excluding &lt;a href=\"Spell%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;spells&lt;/a&gt;, by 20% if the wearer is at or below 30% of their maximum &lt;a href=\"Health%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;HP&lt;/a&gt;."}
