ith a &lt;a href=\"Blessed%20Gem\"&gt;Blessed Gem&lt;/a&gt;, the shield is largely useful for providing players with an early form of heal-over-time on a parrying tool, which can help somewhat in single player. However, as the player eventually obtains other sources of Blessed Gems, this advantage is eventually eclipsed.\nUpgrades.\nReinforced with standard ."}
