{"id": "8347", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8347", "title": "Repairbox", "text": "The Repairbox is a &lt;a href=\"weapon%20modification\"&gt;weapon modification&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"item\"&gt;item&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nGeneral information.\nAllows players to repair their &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;weapons&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Armor%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;armor&lt;/a&gt; at a &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;bonfire&lt;/a&gt;, rather than having to take them to a &lt;a href=\"blacksmith\"&gt;blacksmith&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe Repairbox is one of the few items that does not carry over into &lt;a href=\"New%20Game%20Plus\"&gt;NG+&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "150233", "revid": "296238", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=150233", "title": "Repeat Fire", "text": "Repeat Fire is a &lt;a href=\"skill\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nUpon activation of the skill the player enters a stance, where pressing either R1/RB or R2/RT will fire ten bolts of the chosen variety. These bolts are fired in quick succesion in front of the player, much like the &lt;a href=\"Avelyn%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Avelyn (Dark Souls III)&lt;/a&gt;, and will deal large amounts of damage if all of the bolts connect. \nHowever this skill is best used to roll catch people and should be used sparingly as it will quickly drain your bolts, possibly leaving you with no bolts. One does not need to have ten bolts to use this skill. \nUsage.\nCampaign.\nIn offline play this skill can be put to great use do to enemies usually not dodging, and as such they will likely be hit by all ten arrows dealing large amounts of damage. \nOnline gameplay.\nIn pvp it can be used to roll catch people due to the many hitboxes. It should be noted that it will quickly drain all of your bolts if used often. "}
