{"id": "58030", "revid": "56333033", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=58030", "title": "Resonant Weapon", "text": "Resonant Weapon is a &lt;a href=\"Hexes\"&gt;hex&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nSold by &lt;a href=\"Felkin%20the%20Outcast\"&gt;Felkin the Outcast&lt;/a&gt; for 4,000 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt;.\nGeneral Information.\nSimilar to the effects of &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Weapon\"&gt;Dark Weapon&lt;/a&gt;, casting Resonant Weapon grants an extra 50 &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt; damage to the enchanted weapon. However, like &lt;a href=\"Resonant%20Flesh\"&gt;Resonant Flesh&lt;/a&gt;, the Dark Bonus boost depends on the amount of souls held at the time of casting. Should the player possess little to no souls when casting the spell, then they will only gain a 10% boost, alternatively, when cast with 2,000 souls, the player gains a boost of 50%. Upon casting the hex, 2,000 souls will be consumed. If less than 2,000 souls are in the player's possession, they will all be consumed.\nThe duration of this spell only depends on Faith and ranges from 18 seconds when spiced down to 12 Faith all the way up to 72 seconds at 36 Faith. \nAttunement Milestones.\nLike all other spells, the amount of casts per slot increases upon reaching certain &lt;a href=\"Attunement%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Attunement&lt;/a&gt; milestones:\nDuration Scaling Information.\nDuration values are listed in seconds. Base duration of this spell only depends on Faith. Base duration shown as well as values with the &lt;a href=\"Lingering%20Dragoncrest%20Ring%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Lingering Dragoncrest&lt;/a&gt; variants applied and pieces of &lt;a href=\"Northwarder%20Set\"&gt;Northwarder Set&lt;/a&gt; applied. "}
