{"id": "57547", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=57547", "title": "Ring of Life Protection", "text": "The Ring of Life Protection is a &lt;a href=\"Rings%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;ring&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nEffect.\nPrevents the loss of &lt;a href=\"Health%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;health&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; upon &lt;a href=\"death\"&gt;death&lt;/a&gt;, but breaks. Once broken, it can be repaired for 3,000 souls at a blacksmith. In \"Scholar of the First Sin\", the cost is increased to 14,000 souls."}
{"id": "47660", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=47660", "title": "Ring of Prayer", "text": "The\u00a0Ring of Prayer\u00a0is a\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Rings%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;ring&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nThe Ring of Prayer can be bought from\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Licia%20of%20Lindeldt\"&gt;Licia of Lindeldt&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0for 28,000 souls.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Ring of Prayer increases the &lt;a href=\"Faith%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Faith&lt;/a&gt; stat by five points. This can be useful for players that want to temporarily access certain miracles or equipment that require too much Faith for their current base value. It will also boost the damage of miracles and equipment with Faith &lt;a href=\"Parameter%20Bonus%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;scaling&lt;/a&gt;.\nHowever, it does\u00a0\"not\" contribute to the level requirements for special dialogue with NPCs, such as accessing &lt;a href=\"Felkin%20the%20Outcast\"&gt;Felkin&lt;/a&gt;'s wares or being gifted &lt;a href=\"Licia%20of%20Lindeldt\"&gt;Licia&lt;/a&gt;'s equipment. This is also true for all other stat-boosting equipment."}
