{"id": "135186", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135186", "title": "Evangelist Set", "text": "The Evangelist Set is a &lt;a href=\"Medium%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;medium armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nDrops from the &lt;a href=\"Evangelist\"&gt;Evangelist&lt;/a&gt;s in the &lt;a href=\"Undead%20Settlement\"&gt;Undead Settlement&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Cathedral%20of%20the%20Deep\"&gt;Cathedral of the Deep&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Irithyll%20of%20the%20Boreal%20Valley\"&gt;Irithyll of the Boreal Valley&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Evangelist Set is an unusual cloth set that provides strong all-round defenses, with the most powerful and efficient defenses centered on the chest piece. It is particularly resistant to Strike damage and can reasonably tolerate &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; damage, making it somewhat counter to plate armor sets that are normally weak to those damage types. However, the Evangelist Set is particularly weak to &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt; damage, and has sub-optimal &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt; for its weight."}
