{"id": "4362", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4362", "title": "Fang Boar Helm", "text": "&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;\nThe Fang Boar Helm is a &lt;a href=\"head%20armor\"&gt;head armor&lt;/a&gt; piece in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nThe Fang Boar Helm is a common drop from &lt;a href=\"Fang%20Boar\"&gt;Fang Boar&lt;/a&gt;s, although only three of them appear per playthrough (one at the beginning of the &lt;a href=\"Undead%20Parish\"&gt;Undead Parish&lt;/a&gt; and two in &lt;a href=\"Anor%20Londo\"&gt;Anor Londo&lt;/a&gt;, near the entrance of &lt;a href=\"The%20Duke%27s%20Archives\"&gt;The Duke's Archives&lt;/a&gt;).\nCharacteristics.\nThe Fang Boar Helm is a very heavy helm that provides high &lt;a href=\"physical%20defense\"&gt;physical defense&lt;/a&gt;, poor &lt;a href=\"elemental\"&gt;elemental&lt;/a&gt; defense, and some resistances. At 8.0, it is the heaviest \"standard\" helm, behind only the &lt;a href=\"Symbol%20of%20Avarice\"&gt;Symbol of Avarice&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt can potentially be found very early, making it the first piece of &lt;a href=\"Heavy%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Heavy Armor&lt;/a&gt; the player finds. It is a good helm to use early game, when most enemies only deal physical damage.\nOnce fully upgraded, it has very high physical defense (40.3 average) and the highest &lt;a href=\"Slash\"&gt;Slash&lt;/a&gt; Defense of any &lt;a href=\"Head%20Armor\"&gt;headpiece&lt;/a&gt;, but its elemental defenses remain extremely low.\nUpgrades.\nRequires 200 &lt;a href=\"soul\"&gt;soul&lt;/a&gt;s per upgrade.\n&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;"}
