{"id": "140211", "revid": "33084951", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=140211", "title": "Feast Bell", "text": "Feast Bell is a &lt;a href=\"skill\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nUpon use, the wielder holds up the axe and rings the bell in the center twice. Doing so grants the weapon a &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;bleed&lt;/a&gt; buildup of 55, and causes all attacks to restore 28 &lt;a href=\"Hit%20Points%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;HP&lt;/a&gt; per successful hit on a target."}
{"id": "155392", "revid": "33084951", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=155392", "title": "Feasting Branch", "text": "Feasting Branch is a &lt;a href=\"skill\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nThe player conjures a magic branch in the weapon's hand and proceeds to stab downward very quickly, inflicting 1.2 times the staff's &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Buff\"&gt;Spell Buff&lt;/a&gt; as &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; damage with each strike. This attack can be repeated for as long as the player has &lt;a href=\"Focus%20Points\"&gt;FP&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Endurance%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;stamina&lt;/a&gt;.\nUsage.\nSingle player.\nAs this skill costs FP to perform, it can unnecessarily drain resources in a situation where simply pulling out a melee weapon would be more efficient.\nOnline gameplay.\nThis skill is a very useful way to fend off players that manage to get within melee range to attack, as casters will often otherwise have to pull out a weapon to defend themselves. This skill instead allows the player to tune their loadout purely for spell-casting, and use the skill to fight at melee range."}
{"id": "7159", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=7159", "title": "Feather Arrow", "text": "Feather Arrows are an &lt;a href=\"ammunition\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; type in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nGeneral information.\nFeather Arrows have more &lt;a href=\"range\"&gt;range&lt;/a&gt; than other arrow types, and fly at a faster velocity, meaning that they reach their target earlier. They deal more damage than &lt;a href=\"Standard%20Arrow\"&gt;Standard Arrow&lt;/a&gt;s, and at long range are more powerful than &lt;a href=\"Large%20Arrow\"&gt;Large Arrow&lt;/a&gt;s due to being less susceptible to damage fall-off."}
{"id": "135569", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135569", "title": "Feather Arrow (Dark Souls III)", "text": "Feather Arrows are a type of &lt;a href=\"Ammunition%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nSold by the &lt;a href=\"Shrine%20Handmaid\"&gt;Shrine Handmaid&lt;/a&gt; for 100 &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; each after giving her the &lt;a href=\"Dreamchaser%27s%20Ashes\"&gt;Dreamchaser's Ashes&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nFeather Arrows deal less damage than all other &lt;a href=\"physical%20damage\"&gt;physical damage&lt;/a&gt; arrows, with the exception of the &lt;a href=\"Wood%20Arrow%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Wood Arrow&lt;/a&gt;. However, it makes up for this with its increased &lt;a href=\"range\"&gt;range&lt;/a&gt;, allowing players to deal increased damage to targets that are farther away."}
