{"id": "41950", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=41950", "title": "Fire Arrow (Dark Souls II)", "text": "Fire Arrows are a type of\u00a0 in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nSold by\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Weaponsmith%20Ornifex\"&gt;Weaponsmith Ornifex&lt;/a&gt; for 60 souls each.\nEffect.\nDeals 160 points of &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; damage, plus 50 physical damage.\nIf it can be avoided, don't use these arrows on a purely physically damaging bow, as splitting damage types can severely harm your damage; &lt;a href=\"Iron%20Arrow\"&gt;Iron Arrows&lt;/a&gt; would be a much better choice. A bow that deals fire damage is an excellent fit such as a bow that is fire &lt;a href=\"Infusion\"&gt;Infus&lt;/a&gt;ed.\nFire Arrows can also be used to blow up barrels which can deal large damage to enemies and destroy walls to open up shortcuts such as the one near &lt;a href=\"Steady%20Hand%20McDuff\"&gt;Steady Hand McDuff's&lt;/a&gt; workshop. They can also be used to ignite oil patches from a distance, which can be useful in &lt;a href=\"The%20Gutter\"&gt;The Gutter&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Black%20Gulch\"&gt;Black Gulch&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "130406", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=130406", "title": "Fire Arrow (Dark Souls III)", "text": "Fire Arrows are a type of &lt;a href=\"Ammunition%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nEffect.\nFire Arrows deal minimal &lt;a href=\"Thrust%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;thrust&lt;/a&gt; damage, as well as adding some &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; damage to each shot. They can be useful for applying Fire damage to distant targets, such as staggering a &lt;a href=\"Pus%20of%20Man\"&gt;Pus of Man&lt;/a&gt; or igniting a stack of gunpowder barrels."}
{"id": "69798", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=69798", "title": "Fire Bolt", "text": "Fire Bolts are a type of &lt;a href=\"Ammunition%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nSold by\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Weaponsmith%20Ornifex\"&gt;Weaponsmith Ornifex&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0for 80 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; each.\nEffect.\nDeals 160 points of &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; damage, plus 70 &lt;a href=\"physical%20damage\"&gt;physical damage&lt;/a&gt;."}
