{"id": "52363", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=52363", "title": "Fire Greatarrow", "text": "Fire Greatarrows are a type of &lt;a href=\"Ammunition%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nUsage.\nFire Greatarrows deal split &lt;a href=\"physical\"&gt;physical&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;fire&lt;/a&gt; damage, making them an attractive addition to any players' arsenal, as enemies that are weak to fire will take considerably more damage from each greatarrow, and the split damage makes them harder to block against (unless a &lt;a href=\"Gyrm%20Greatshield\"&gt;Gyrm Greatshield&lt;/a&gt; is in use).\nThey do travel slower, however, and will do noticeably less damage to enemies that are resistant to fire damage. &lt;a href=\"Greatbows\"&gt;Greatbows&lt;/a&gt; infused with &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;fire&lt;/a&gt; will benefit greatly from the use of these greatarrows."}
