{"id": "135190", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135190", "title": "Fire Keeper Set", "text": "The Fire Keeper Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound on a corpse by dropping off the bridge in front of the lift in the tower containing the &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Keeper%20Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Fire Keeper Soul&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Firelink%20Shrine%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Firelink Shrine&lt;/a&gt;.\nInstead of jumping safely to the casket on the right (when looking at the lift), look to the left of the bridge and there will be a dead body visible below. Jumping toward it will most likely make the player miss their footing and sustain massive fall damage as a consequence, killing them even at maxed out &lt;a href=\"Vigor%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Vigor&lt;/a&gt; and with the &lt;a href=\"Silvercat%20Ring%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Silvercat Ring&lt;/a&gt; equipped. It's recommended just to run off instead of jumping.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Fire Keeper Set has poor defenses all-around. Its greatest assets are its &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt; absorption, combined with its light &lt;a href=\"weight\"&gt;weight&lt;/a&gt;. It is particularly weak to &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"buildup\"&gt;buildup&lt;/a&gt;."}
